title: Richwell Group, Inc. Recalls Siluriformes Products  Produced Without Benefit of Import Inspection

impacted_products: 14-oz. clear bag packages containing “Maxfield Seafood SHEAT FISH CA TREN KET” with “EXPIRY DATE” of 191031 through 201227.
